557
01:01:22,883 --> 01:01:24,996
<i>The worms stir against my mother...</i>

558
01:01:24,997 --> 01:01:27,185
<i>wind of the roses,
wind of the mud...</i>

559
01:01:27,285 --> 01:01:30,018
<i>echo gives no answer...
follow my lonely fingers,</i>

560
01:01:30,118 --> 01:01:33,796
<i>follow my absent image...
I am the rector of no mind...</i>

561
01:01:33,896 --> 01:01:37,136
<i>the lonesomest fingers in the world...
the cornerstones of my heart</i>

562
01:01:37,236 --> 01:01:38,988
<i>bring about nothing...
whispering of a ghost...</i>

563
01:01:39,089 --> 01:01:42,083
<i>she doesn't know I'm scared...
