Fabulous man!

637
01:12:30,556 --> 01:12:33,222
Keep the wine flowing, please.

638
01:12:33,347 --> 01:12:35,389
This is going to cost
an ram and a leg.

639
01:12:35,431 --> 01:12:36,431
Who cares?

