703
01:18:22,787 --> 01:18:27,513
<i>but everything here is gray:
my feelings,</i>

704
01:18:27,548 --> 01:18:31,953
<i>the people, even Eugene.</i>

705
01:18:32,078 --> 01:18:36,036
<i>Europe is nothing but a false promise.</i>

706
01:18:36,036 --> 01:18:38,953
<i>Half of me is missing, Jack.</i>

707
01:18:39,286 --> 01:18:42,578
