714
01:19:02,952 --> 01:19:05,460
Don't be coy. 
Let me read it.

715
01:19:05,461 --> 01:19:07,162
- No, it's not finished.
- Let me see it.

716
01:19:07,262 --> 01:19:10,897
- Let me read it.
